I am in such a shitty mood. I really cant stand life the way it is now. Im being so honest i want to scream. I hate how certain people either avoid me or dont like me because I have a boyfriend. I dont understand that. I Hate how I am at the mental level of 18 or 19 and cant enjoy being young. Everything just plain sucks. I feel like I dont belong anywhere. maybe i dont. this will probably be neverending. I hate how almost no one seems to care whats really going on with me and I hate being treated like shit just because I dont talk alot in school. fuck them, im not shy, i just hate school. 

I will do everyone a favor once i can just leave. Let go of all the shit that has fucked with my mind so much over the years. I hate family. I hate doing the same thing every fucking day. Im not gonna go and kill myself though, I am just having a semi breakdown. What i need is a drink to forget.

My whole body aches and I have nothing to do. I hate the way I am, I just fucking hate myself.

Its tuesday, this week is going by very slow which is good. My piercing is healing pretty good, surprizingly.  I am really glad I got it, dont regret it at all, the only thing that sucks is i cant really move around a lot but oh well. I got so many gift certificates yesterday from aunts and stuff, think i might go spend them today.

I cant wait until summer, no more cold, 16 birthday, driving. ah.

Christmas went by fast, it didnt even feel like it was christmas. Im bored. I saw sarah yesterday.. 
Im getting alot more sleep now, not like last week. well i cant really think of any thing else to ramble about so yeah.

I got my belly button pierced today. I like it, i dont really give a fuck if everybody has it. and it will only take 2 months to heal. I have pictures but i dont know how to add them here. It didnt hurt that bad, only for a few seconds. I want to get more piercings now, ears next yay!

Christmas was pretty boring, family shit.

Im so thrilled its vacation.

hmmm not much to say for now.

my computer is fucking up.
went home sick today, missed a lot but i dont really care. 1 more day till vacation finally. well im going to go lay down.

Its early, I cant sleep. I still have much anger. Im supposed to see my dad today but i dont really feel like it.. ugh. Mike is ruining my weekend. FUCK HIM. anyways, im very tired, didnt get that much sleep again which sucks. father got his new house in downtown simsbury, it reminds me of a place where people get murdered but maybe thats just me.. well im gonna try to sleep again, I NEED the rest.

Haha He totally ruined my good mood. wait no I was already in a bad mood so this just is wonderful, really I am exstatic, everything is so great I couldnt ask for more Haha. really. wow i am so angry. I feel like going downstairs and smashing Mikes face in.

not a bad idea..

I hate how I cant control my anger latly, i hate these mood swings, theres a word for it that I was "diagnosed" as but I forgot. Im forgetting alot of things latly. I want a drink. wow I am being so random, Probably the lack of sleep. ugh I need to take a walk.
my computer is too slow and fucked up to write a full entry so ill just say this... i'm going to buy my very own computer ASAP so then i can update more etc.

Homecoming is on saturday, i dont really want to go, personally, i think its stupid and no, im not being apathetic or anti-social I just think its pointless. Sure ill go to prom but not homecoming besides i dont have a dress.

I think im almost out of therapy, i just have to talk to one more person, i wont even bother with my father, its pointless so ill just act like everythings fine with daddy dearest..

School is ok, im actually doing pretty well in my classes which is a surprise.

I decided finally that im going to get my belly button pierced, tongue pierced, and my tattoo, i hope i can get at least 1 done soon.

Im also getting pretty good at driving which means im closer to getting a liscence but im not going to get the car i wanted anymore, long story and besides i doubt anyones reading this anyways.

other than that everything is the same. Sarah hasnt called, i guess moving made her forget about me. oh well im not going to waste my energy on that, she wont change.

My personality is changing a little bit, i think its for the better, im not as weak anymore i think, actually this could just be a mood swing of happiness which will go away in a few days, im used to it.

im having a panic attack right now, i got upstairs and i couldnt breath, after getting water, i started breathing really fast and i cant walk that well, i almost fell down the stairs. i took some of my klonopin but it hasnt kicked in yet. i wish that i could be normal. why do i have to have all this shit? i mean i know that the world is fucked up but what did i do to deserve all of this? and no i am not whining. Ive had these panic attackes alot but they have been getting worse over the days almost as bad as they where last year. ugh im overheating and still cant breath right. i want this to be over, what the hell can i do to make it stop. i did some reading on the shit that i have and it is really depressing. yeah shit room is spinning, have to go. I wish i could make the pain go away.

went to salem yesterday with richie, boston next week. it was good. we basicaly walked around the whole time and took a couple shitty tours that were a waste of money. overall, it was fun though, not what i expected. the meds for anxiety work, which is a good thing because i have had more panic attacks latly. theres really nothing that i can do about the other two things tho unless i go on anti depressents or mood levelers which i am against so yeah i guess ill just have to deal with it like i have been for years. whatever i dont really care either way. right now i guess im in a good mood but it wont last the whole day. o well im used to it. I didnt get good sleep last night because dave, brother, was screaming and yelling, fucking bastard, i can never get any goddamn sleep in this house. good news is they leave for vacation next week! bad news is that i have to stay at my dads for half the time.ugh i have to go now, shit to do. :/

yeah i went to a shrink doctor guy today and found out that i am extremly fucked up!! yup i have OCD and i am bi-polor and i am borderline. great huh? yeah so he prescribed meds for anxiety so when i have a panic attack, i wont go into one of my manic cleaning things. yeah well i have to leave now, ill write more later...
